revision.text:
{{Chess Opening Theory/Position|= |Greco Defence| |rd|nd|bd||kd|bd|nd|rd|= |pd|pd|pd|pd| |pd|pd|pd|= | | | | | |qd| | |= | | | | |pd| | | |= | | | | |pl| | | |= | | | | | |nl| | |= |pl|pl|pl|pl| |pl|pl|pl|= |rl|nl|bl|ql|kl|bl| |rl|= || }} = Greco Defence = ===2...Qf6=== Moves: :[[/3. Bc4/]]
The Greco Defence attempts to defend Black's e-Pawn with the Queen. This defence is rarely seen professionally as White is provided an advantage in development.
