== Barnes Opening/Fool's Mate ==
===2... Qh4#===
White has played a very poor move and allowed Black the quickest possible checkmate&nbsp;&ndash; [[Fool's Mate]] &ndash; in the opening game of chess: Mate in two moves.  The mate almost never occurs in practice but is commonly known among chess players, due to it being the fastest possible checkmate.

A variation of this mate occurs when White advances the f-pawn two squares: '''1. f4 e6 2. g4 Qh4#'''. White can also move his g-pawn before the f-pawn.

